{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Satan, evil incarnate, has undertaken the nefarious deed of stealing the Gutenberg Bible, a book destined to be copied by the newly invented printing press and spread across the known world. This alteration of events has allowed evil to clutch ever tighter and has kept the word of the Bible from stirring mankind toward its message.<br><br>It falls to you, a noble Paladin, to undertake the quest to retrieve this book and to keep the darkness at bay. In this quest, you will explore complex dungeons that are filled with ancient puzzles left behind to challenge your intellect. Your quest will span many worldwide locations such as under the Sphinx, in Scottish castles, and inside Mayan ruins, all filled with hidden chambers and secrets.  <br><br>Test your strength against many horrific creatures with an arsenal of holy weapons at your side. You have a chance to bend history back against the will of Satan, sending his minions into oblivion with high intensity First-Person action. However, returning the Gutenberg Bible back to its rightful place will not be an easy quest!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Acquire Spiritual Armor and an array of divine weaponry.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore complex dungeons, mazes, puzzles, and secret quests!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Obtain the mantle of Paladin and defeat the ultimate evil!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Journey to numerous locations around the world! Find helpful angels hidden along your path.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fast-paced First-Person action!</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319590/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735134375","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319590/page.bg.jpg?t=1735134375","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319590/bb97ff88a7dd9a3ca81b7fd7774dcde8be3b83af/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735134375","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319590/bb97ff88a7dd9a3ca81b7fd7774dcde8be3b83af/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735134375","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Satan, evil incarnate, has undertaken the nefarious deed of stealing the Gutenberg Bible, a book destined to be copied by the newly invented printing press and spread across the known world. This alteration of events has allowed evil to clutch ever tighter and has kept the word of the Bible from stirring mankind toward its message.<br><br>It falls to you, a noble Paladin, to undertake the quest to retrieve this book and to keep the darkness at bay. In this quest, you will explore complex dungeons that are filled with ancient puzzles left behind to challenge your intellect. Your quest will span many worldwide locations such as under the Sphinx, in Scottish castles, and inside Mayan ruins, all filled with hidden chambers and secrets.  <br><br>Test your strength against many horrific creatures with an arsenal of holy weapons at your side. You have a chance to bend history back against the will of Satan, sending his minions into oblivion with high intensity First-Person action. However, returning the Gutenberg Bible back to its rightful place will not be an easy quest!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Acquire Spiritual Armor and an array of divine weaponry.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore complex dungeons, mazes, puzzles, and secret quests!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Obtain the mantle of Paladin and defeat the ultimate evil!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Journey to numerous locations around the world! Find helpful angels hidden along your path.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fast-paced First-Person action!</p></li></ul>","developers":["N'Lightning Software Development","Jordan Freeman Group"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319590/header.jpg?t=1735134375","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"\u00a9 2001-2024 N'Lightning Software Development, Inc. and Jordan Freeman Group, LLC (DBA: ZOOM Platform). All Rights Reserved.","linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257071058,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257071058/movie480.mp4?t=1731058488","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257071058/movie_max.mp4?t=1731058488"},"name":"Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257071058/7ce9e23c937e52b183a46e75594fe7233051322d/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1731058488","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257071058/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1731058488","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257071058/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1731058488"}}],"name":"Ominous Horizons: A Paladin's Calling","package_groups":[{"description":"","display_type":0,"is_recurring_subscription":"false","name":"default","save_text":"","selection_text":"Select a purchase option","subs":[{"can_get_free_license":"0","is_free_license":false,"option_description":"","option_text":"Ominous Horizons: A Paladin's Calling - $9.99 USD","packageid":1175414,"percent_savings":0,"percent_savings_text":" ","price_in_cents_with_discount":999}],"title":"Buy Ominous Horizons: A Paladin's Calling"}],"packages":[1175414],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> WIndows 10 / 11<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> Version 9.0c<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 400 MB availab